<c.japanese>&lrm;悪事は 恨みを買うもの！</c.japanese>

149
00:06:45,029 --> 00:06:47,698
<c.japanese>&lrm;若く力のあるうちは
&lrm;好き放題できても</c.japanese>

150
00:06:47,782 --> 00:06:50,576
<c.japanese>&lrm;老い衰えば
&lrm;奪い合いに勝てずに飢え</c.japanese>

151
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:54,872
<c.japanese>&lrm;かつての悪行の報復におびえて
&lrm;暮らすことになるだろう！</c.japanese>

152
00:06:54,956 --> 00:06:56,332
<c.japanese>&lrm;（頭領）はあ？</c.japanese>

153
00:06:56,416 --> 00:07:01,087
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たま）しかし 皆が剣を捨て
&lrm;互助と博愛の世となれば</c.japanese>

154
00:07:01,170 --> 00:07:04,090
<c.japanese>&lrm;斬らず 斬られず
&lrm;とらず とられず</c.japanese>

155
00:07:04,173 --> 00:07:05,591
<c.japanese>&lrm;分け合えば 飢えず</c.japanese>

156
00:07:06,217 --> 00:07:10,221
<c.japanese>&lrm;老後も安心
&lrm;楽々満腹生活となるという寸法！</c.japanese>

157
00:07:10,304 --> 00:07:12,765
<c.japanese>&lrm;どうだ！　この完全理論！</c.japanese>

158
00:07:12,849 --> 00:07:14,225
<c.japanese>&lrm;フハハハ…</c.japanese>

159
00:07:14,308 --> 00:07:17,895
<c.japanese>&lrm;ウハハハ… ウハハハ…</c.japanese>

160
00:07:17,979 --> 00:07:19,814
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）&lrm;本気か？</c.japanese>

161
00:07:19,897 --> 00:07:22,733
<c.japanese>&lrm;こいつ それを言うために ここに？</c.japanese>

162
00:07:22,817 --> 00:07:24,485
<c.japanese>&lrm;（野武士）黙って聞いてりゃ</c.japanese>

163
00:07:24,569 --> 00:07:26,320
<c.japanese>&lrm;グダグダ グダグダ
&lrm;何言ってやがる…</c.japanese>

164
00:07:26,404 --> 00:07:27,238
<c.japanese>&lrm;（野武士たち）うわ～</c.japanese>

165
00:07:28,531 --> 00:07:30,116
<c.japanese>&lrm;ほら 無駄でしょう？</c.japanese>

166
00:07:30,199 --> 00:07:32,368
<c.japanese>&lrm;人など 捨て置けばいいのです</c.japanese>

167
00:07:32,452 --> 00:07:35,913
<c.japanese>&lrm;いいかげん
&lrm;その人嫌いと短気を直せ</c.japanese>

168
00:07:35,997 --> 00:07:36,998
<c.japanese>&lrm;おかげで また…</c.japanese>

169
00:07:37,081 --> 00:07:38,749
<c.japanese>&lrm;（頭領）やれ
&lrm;（野武士たち）うお～</c.japanese>

170
00:07:38,833 --> 00:07:41,377
<c.japanese>&lrm;（野武士たち）おっ!?
&lrm;（たま）説得し損ねたではないか</c.japanese>

171
00:07:41,461 --> 00:07:43,880
<c.japanese>&lrm;（野武士たち）うわ～</c.japanese>

172
00:07:45,423 --> 00:07:46,382
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）&lrm;すげえ</c.japanese>

173
00:07:47,049 --> 00:07:51,012
<c.japanese>&lrm;鬼兜組っていったら
&lrm;ここら辺じゃ 敵なしの連中なのに</c.japanese>

174
00:07:51,637 --> 00:07:53,514
<c.japanese>&lrm;（野武士）おりゃ～！</c.japanese>

175
00:07:53,598 --> 00:07:54,891
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）うっ… ああっ
&lrm;（野武士）ああっ</c.japanese>

176
00:07:53,598 --> 00:07:54,891
<c.japanese>（野武士）うわっ</c.japanese>

177
00:07:54,974 --> 00:07:57,768
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）
&lrm;ああっ… ふっ くっ… ううっ</c.japanese>

178
00:07:57,852 --> 00:07:59,103
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）ああっ…
&lrm;（野武士）うう…</c.japanese>

179
00:07:59,187 --> 00:08:00,021
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）うっ くっ</c.japanese>

180
00:08:00,646 --> 00:08:03,566
<c.japanese>&lrm;うっ うっ… ぐっ…</c.japanese>

181
00:08:03,649 --> 00:08:04,609
<c.japanese>&lrm;うわあああああっ…</c.japanese>

182
00:08:04,609 --> 00:08:05,526
<c.japanese>&lrm;うわあああああっ…</c.japanese>

183
00:08:04,609 --> 00:08:05,526
<c.japanese>（野武士）んっ？</c.japanese>

184
00:08:05,526 --> 00:08:07,862
<c.japanese>&lrm;うわあああああっ…</c.japanese>

185
00:08:08,696 --> 00:08:09,989
<c.japanese>&lrm;うっ！</c.japanese>

186
00:08:16,245 --> 00:08:17,622
<c.japanese>&lrm;がはっ…</c.japanese>

187
00:08:19,999 --> 00:08:22,251
<c.japanese>&lrm;ハァ ハァ…</c.japanese>

188
00:08:22,335 --> 00:08:24,378
<c.japanese>&lrm;なんと… 兜割りだと？</c.japanese>

189
00:08:25,588 --> 00:08:28,799
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）き… き… 斬った 斬れた</c.japanese>

190
00:08:28,883 --> 00:08:30,384
<c.japanese>&lrm;よし これなら…</c.japanese>

191
00:08:31,093 --> 00:08:33,012
<c.japanese>&lrm;兵頭真介 参る！</c.japanese>

192
00:08:33,596 --> 00:08:35,264
<c.japanese>&lrm;鬼兜 覚悟！</c.japanese>

193
00:08:35,348 --> 00:08:42,063
<c.japanese>&lrm;せいやあああああああっ…</c.japanese>

194
00:08:42,688 --> 00:08:46,984
<c.japanese>&lrm;うおおおおっ…</c.japanese>

195
00:08:47,485 --> 00:08:48,945
<c.japanese>&lrm;ぐっ！</c.japanese>

196
00:08:49,028 --> 00:08:50,446
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）なっ…
&lrm;（たま･迅火）あっ</c.japanese>

197
00:08:53,783 --> 00:08:55,243
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）んなあっ…</c.japanese>

198
00:08:55,326 --> 00:08:56,577
<c.japanese>&lrm;あっ ぐっ… うっ</c.japanese>

199
00:09:00,331 --> 00:09:02,458
<c.japanese>&lrm;（兜の闇(かたわら)）思わず正体見せちまった</c.japanese>

200
00:09:02,542 --> 00:09:03,584
<c.japanese>&lrm;（野武士）頭領…</c.japanese>

201
00:09:03,668 --> 00:09:04,835
<c.japanese>&lrm;（野武士）化け物だ</c.japanese>

202
00:09:04,919 --> 00:09:06,837
<c.japanese>&lrm;（兜の闇）てめえら 黙れ！</c.japanese>

203
00:09:06,921 --> 00:09:09,715
<c.japanese>&lrm;逃げ出すやつも ぶっ殺すぞ！</c.japanese>

204
00:09:10,508 --> 00:09:11,592
<c.japanese>&lrm;闇か</c.japanese>

205
00:09:11,676 --> 00:09:13,135
<c.japanese>&lrm;闇？</c.japanese>

206
00:09:13,219 --> 00:09:14,762
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）
&lrm;魍魎(もうりょう)&lrm; 亡霊 変化(へんげ) 人外の総称</c.japanese>

207
00:09:14,762 --> 00:09:15,680
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）
&lrm;魍魎(もうりょう)&lrm; 亡霊 変化(へんげ) 人外の総称</c.japanese>

208
00:09:14,762 --> 00:09:15,680
<c.japanese>（真介）あっ</c.japanese>

209
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,515
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）
&lrm;魍魎(もうりょう)&lrm; 亡霊 変化(へんげ) 人外の総称</c.japanese>

210
00:09:17,598 --> 00:09:19,976
<c.japanese>&lrm;傍(そば)&lrm;にある者 それが闇</c.japanese>

211
00:09:20,059 --> 00:09:21,394
<c.japanese>&lrm;倒せるか？</c.japanese>

212
00:09:21,477 --> 00:09:24,438
<c.japanese>&lrm;隠形(おんぎょう)&lrm;の達者なのは強いですからね</c.japanese>

213
00:09:24,522 --> 00:09:25,731
<c.japanese>&lrm;精霊転化(せいれいてんげ)&lrm;なら</c.japanese>

214
00:09:25,815 --> 00:09:27,608
<c.japanese>&lrm;精霊転化？</c.japanese>

215
00:09:27,692 --> 00:09:28,693
<c.japanese>&lrm;よし</c.japanese>

216
00:09:28,776 --> 00:09:33,364
<c.japanese>&lrm;ただ 闇を殴り倒すのは
&lrm;良心の呵責(かしゃく)が…</c.japanese>

217
00:09:33,447 --> 00:09:38,119
<c.japanese>&lrm;闇であれ 人間であれ
&lrm;非道の者は 断つ！</c.japanese>

218
00:09:38,202 --> 00:09:40,871
<c.japanese>&lrm;（兜の闇）恥かかせやがって</c.japanese>

219
00:09:40,955 --> 00:09:44,250
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）ああっ うぐっ ああっ…
&lrm;（兜の闇）皆殺しだ～！</c.japanese>

220
00:09:45,918 --> 00:09:47,044
<c.japanese>&lrm;んっ</c.japanese>

221
00:09:55,052 --> 00:09:55,886
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）では</c.japanese>

222
00:10:01,726 --> 00:10:02,727
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たま）あっ…</c.japanese>

223
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,747
<c.japanese>&lrm;な… 何だ？</c.japanese>

224
00:10:22,830 --> 00:10:24,665
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たま）精霊転化</c.japanese>

225
00:10:24,749 --> 00:10:30,004
<c.japanese>&lrm;闇の霊力に同調し
&lrm;己を闇へと近付ける秘術</c.japanese>

226
00:10:30,087 --> 00:10:31,922
<c.japanese>&lrm;精霊体となった迅火は</c.japanese>

227
00:10:32,006 --> 00:10:33,341
<c.japanese>&lrm;無敵だ</c.japanese>

228
00:10:33,424 --> 00:10:34,425
<c.japanese>&lrm;無敵？</c.japanese>

229
00:10:34,508 --> 00:10:37,928
<c.japanese>&lrm;殺せ！
&lrm;殺されたくなかったら 殺せ！</c.japanese>

230
00:10:38,012 --> 00:10:40,181
<c.japanese>&lrm;（野武士たち）うお～！</c.japanese>

231
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:44,935
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）ふっ
&lrm;（野武士たち）うわ～</c.japanese>

232
00:10:48,731 --> 00:10:50,566
<c.japanese>&lrm;ホント すみませんね</c.japanese>

233
00:10:50,649 --> 00:10:54,320
<c.japanese>&lrm;人間は いくら集めても
&lrm;しょせん人間か</c.japanese>

234
00:10:54,403 --> 00:10:57,323
<c.japanese>&lrm;珍しい目だな 食ってやる！</c.japanese>

235
00:10:57,406 --> 00:10:59,950
<c.japanese>&lrm;あの杖で戦うってのか？</c.japanese>

236
00:11:00,034 --> 00:11:01,202
<c.japanese>&lrm;黙って見ていろ</c.japanese>

237
00:11:06,248 --> 00:11:09,460
<c.japanese>&lrm;（兜の闇）ふっ やあっ…</c.japanese>

238
00:11:11,712 --> 00:11:13,381
<c.japanese>&lrm;ふんっ</c.japanese>

239
00:11:13,464 --> 00:11:16,842
<c.japanese>&lrm;うああああっ…</c.japanese>

240
00:11:18,302 --> 00:11:20,054
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）ううっ！
&lrm;（兜の闇）んん…</c.japanese>

241
00:11:20,137 --> 00:11:21,055
<c.japanese>&lrm;またか</c.japanese>

242
00:11:21,138 --> 00:11:22,556
<c.japanese>&lrm;（兜の闇）フフフ…</c.japanese>

243
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:25,559
<c.japanese>&lrm;残念ながら 腕は
&lrm;もう２本あるんだよ</c.japanese>

244
00:11:25,643 --> 00:11:26,977
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）んっ…</c.japanese>

245
00:11:27,061 --> 00:11:29,688
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）ぬうううおっ…
&lrm;（兜の闇）ふあい！</c.japanese>

246
00:11:29,772 --> 00:11:32,066
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）ううう… おおっ</c.japanese>

247
00:11:32,149 --> 00:11:33,609
<c.japanese>&lrm;（兜の闇）うぐっ…</c.japanese>

248
00:11:41,117 --> 00:11:42,952
<c.japanese>&lrm;つ… 強(つえ)え</c.japanese>

249
00:11:45,121 --> 00:11:45,955
<c.japanese>&lrm;（兜の闇）かっ…</c.japanese>

250
00:11:46,038 --> 00:11:47,248
<c.japanese>&lrm;解</c.japanese>

251
00:11:55,089 --> 00:11:57,508
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たま）死体を操っていたのか</c.japanese>

252
00:11:59,468 --> 00:12:02,972
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）さようなら
&lrm;黄泉路(よみじ)&lrm;に お気を付けて</c.japanese>

253
00:12:18,028 --> 00:12:20,656
<c.japanese>&lrm;なぜ こんなことをしてるんだ？</c.japanese>

254
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:21,699
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たま）ん？</c.japanese>

255
00:12:21,782 --> 00:12:24,744
<c.japanese>&lrm;妖狐と仙道が なぜ こんなことを</c.japanese>

256
00:12:25,661 --> 00:12:26,662
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たま）フフッ…</c.japanese>

257
00:12:29,915 --> 00:12:33,711
<c.japanese>&lrm;おれは 人間が好きなのだ</c.japanese>

258
00:12:33,794 --> 00:12:37,131
<c.japanese>&lrm;故に 悪行撲滅に従事している</c.japanese>

259
00:12:37,715 --> 00:12:40,885
<c.japanese>&lrm;私は無理やり
&lrm;付き合わされているだけですが</c.japanese>

260
00:12:40,968 --> 00:12:43,888
<c.japanese>&lrm;人間が好きな妖狐…</c.japanese>

261
00:12:45,264 --> 00:12:48,267
<c.japanese>&lrm;耳の穴 かっぽじって
&lrm;よ～く聞け！</c.japanese>

262
00:12:48,976 --> 00:12:51,395
<c.japanese>&lrm;我ら 乱世を憂う者</c.japanese>

263
00:12:52,021 --> 00:12:53,439
<c.japanese>&lrm;人呼んで…</c.japanese>

264
00:12:54,732 --> 00:12:56,317
<c.japanese>&lrm;世直し姉弟！</c.japanese>

265
00:12:57,985 --> 00:12:59,904
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）ああ…</c.japanese>

266
00:13:01,697 --> 00:13:04,325
<c.japanese>そ… そうなんだ</c.japanese>

267
00:13:14,001 --> 00:13:16,879
<c.japanese>&lrm;まだついてきますよ
&lrm;まきますか？</c.japanese>

268
00:13:16,962 --> 00:13:17,922
<c.japanese>&lrm;ほっとけ</c.japanese>

269
00:13:19,131 --> 00:13:22,718
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）&lrm;闇…
&lrm;あんなもんがいるなんて</c.japanese>

270
00:13:23,260 --> 00:13:28,182
<c.japanese>&lrm;もしかしたら とんでもない世界を
&lrm;見つけたのかもしれねえ</c.japanese>

271
00:13:29,308 --> 00:13:31,101
<c.japanese>&lrm;あそこに泊まるのか</c.japanese>

272
00:13:31,185 --> 00:13:32,436
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）うっ…</c.japanese>

273
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:34,772
<c.japanese>&lrm;（商人）熊なんてもんじゃねえぞ</c.japanese>

274
00:13:34,855 --> 00:13:35,689
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）ん？</c.japanese>

275
00:13:35,773 --> 00:13:39,109
<c.japanese>&lrm;（商人）とにかく
&lrm;あの街道は やめるんだ</c.japanese>

276
00:13:39,193 --> 00:13:41,195
<c.japanese>&lrm;化け物に殺されちまうぞ</c.japanese>

277
00:13:41,278 --> 00:13:42,696
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）化け物？</c.japanese>

278
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:46,200
<c.japanese>&lrm;そうだ 昼間 街道に現れて…</c.japanese>

279
00:13:47,409 --> 00:13:49,453
<c.japanese>&lrm;（商人）ひい～！
&lrm;（斎練(さいれん)）下がっておれ</c.japanese>

280
00:13:50,538 --> 00:13:53,916
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斎練）我は断怪衆(だんがいしゅう)が一人 斎練</c.japanese>

281
00:13:53,999 --> 00:13:58,462
<c.japanese>&lrm;人食いの闇 灼岩(しゃくがん)よ
&lrm;汝(なんじ)&lrm;を断ちに参った！</c.japanese>

282
00:13:59,088 --> 00:14:00,631
<c.japanese>&lrm;仏罰を浴びよ！</c.japanese>

283
00:14:00,714 --> 00:14:01,715
<c.japanese>&lrm;はあっ！</c.japanese>

284
00:14:05,803 --> 00:14:06,971
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斎練）なっ…
&lrm;（商人）ああ…</c.japanese>

285
00:14:07,054 --> 00:14:08,931
<c.japanese>&lrm;（商人）ああっ あああ…
&lrm;（斎練）あっ</c.japanese>

286
00:14:09,515 --> 00:14:11,475
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斎練）うわっ
&lrm;（衝撃音）</c.japanese>

287
00:14:11,559 --> 00:14:13,102
<c.japanese>&lrm;こんなやつだ</c.japanese>

288
00:14:17,314 --> 00:14:18,524
<c.japanese>&lrm;（印河(いんが)）灼岩だ</c.japanese>

289
00:14:18,607 --> 00:14:19,984
<c.japanese>&lrm;灼岩？</c.japanese>

290
00:14:20,067 --> 00:14:23,779
<c.japanese>&lrm;あっ そういや 斎練とかいう
&lrm;法師様も そんなことを…</c.japanese>

291
00:14:23,863 --> 00:14:25,614
<c.japanese>&lrm;（央鳳(おうほう)）斎練を知っているのか？</c.japanese>

292
00:14:25,698 --> 00:14:27,491
<c.japanese>&lrm;いや まあ そりゃ…</c.japanese>

293
00:14:27,575 --> 00:14:31,120
<c.japanese>&lrm;先ほど やられちまった
&lrm;法師様ってのが…</c.japanese>

294
00:14:31,203 --> 00:14:32,121
